## How to read this list

Each row represents a third-party service we use that may receive or
process personal information collected through {{PROJECT_NAME}}. We are
accountable under PIPEDA for these subprocessors' practices when they
process personal information on our behalf.

| Column | Meaning |
|---|---|
| **Vendor** | Legal name + service. |
| **Data category** | What classes of personal information the vendor processes (account, billing, communications, technical, etc.). |
| **Region** | Where the vendor processes the data (e.g., Canada-only, US, EU, global). |
| **DPA / contract** | Whether a data-processing agreement (or equivalent) is in place. |
| **Notes** | Anything customers should know — sub-subprocessor list URL, SOC 2 report availability, BAA path for health data, etc. |

